---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

export let title = "Privacy Policy";
---

<Layout title={title} description="Understand how we protect your data at Rantique.">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">üîê Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      At Rantique, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Personal information (name, email) if you contact us or subscribe.</li>
      <li>Non-personal data through cookies and analytics tools.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>
      We use your data to provide and improve our content, respond to your inquiries, and send occasional newsletters (if subscribed).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">3. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      Our site uses cookies for basic analytics and site functionality. You can control or disable cookies in your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      We use trusted services like Google Analytics, but we never sell or rent your personal data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission is 100% secure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      You can request to access, update, or delete your personal information by contacting us at any time.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Changes will be posted here with a new effective date.
    </p>

    <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mt-10">
      Effective Date: June 24, 2025
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
